  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Boba Teashop</strong> is a cozy horror game where you own and manage a boba tea shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare boba teas, serve customers, and expand your menu to attract more patrons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/6c59aac69b7e37e9a2d03f9951c2f697.webp?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/4615eb958d8b4b4c46634730fc3178db.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/4615eb958d8b4b4c46634730fc3178db.webm?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/4615eb958d8b4b4c46634730fc3178db.mp4?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Risa, a woman in her 30s who is tired of corporate life and has decided to chase her dream of opening a boba tea shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/3f685c11d3eddb2a0e8dc64bcdf16c3b.webp?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/eadb667dc9800e443351e12f717d40d0.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/eadb667dc9800e443351e12f717d40d0.webm?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/eadb667dc9800e443351e12f717d40d0.mp4?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a boba tea shop owner, you will encounter a variety of customers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your job is to greet them with a smile and take their orders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/682abfa4b58a538318ce9c479acd2107.webp?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/0980534b3249f455a025db49a50d5400.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/0980534b3249f455a025db49a50d5400.webm?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/0980534b3249f455a025db49a50d5400.mp4?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Making boba tea is simple. The ingredients are just milk tea and boba. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seal the cup with a lid and serve it with a straw for sipping and enjoying the boba pearls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/69e7b219a726ab7af3fa0528aafcc7c3.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/69e7b219a726ab7af3fa0528aafcc7c3.webm?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/69e7b219a726ab7af3fa0528aafcc7c3.mp4?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But sometimes, you'll encounter demanding customers with special requests or those who leave a mess in your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the proud owner of a boba tea shop, there's nothing you can't handle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/62b5b3056dbc585299cb4d9b6ce13e70.apng?t=1758094031\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/62b5b3056dbc585299cb4d9b6ce13e70.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=56 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/1c5aa1c0612d023aeecc04dcfb4d9fe7.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/1c5aa1c0612d023aeecc04dcfb4d9fe7.webm?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/1c5aa1c0612d023aeecc04dcfb4d9fe7.mp4?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While serving customers and managing your boba tea shop, you start seeing visions and hearing things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is it all in your head, or is something haunting the place?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is psychological horror game that builds tension through eerie atmosphere, unsettling events, and moments of intense scare when you least expect them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> A simple yet engaging loop where you take orders from customers, prepare their drinks, and serve them with a smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VHS Aesthetics:</strong> Experience the game through a creepy VHS filter that adds a nostalgic and eerie atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story:</strong> Uncover Risa's journey and personal growth as she pursues her dream of becoming a successful boba tea shop owner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For content creators:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to create content from the game and monetize the gameplay by any means. There are no other restrictions from my side when playing the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Boba Teashop</strong> is a cozy horror game where you own and manage a boba tea shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare boba teas, serve customers, and expand your menu to attract more patrons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/6c59aac69b7e37e9a2d03f9951c2f697.webp?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/4615eb958d8b4b4c46634730fc3178db.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/4615eb958d8b4b4c46634730fc3178db.webm?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/4615eb958d8b4b4c46634730fc3178db.mp4?t=1758094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Risa, a woman in her 30s who is tired of corporate life and has decided to chase her dream of opening a boba tea shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/3f685c11d3eddb2a0e8dc64bcdf16c3b.webp?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/eadb667dc9800e443351e12f717d40d0.poster.avif?t=1758094031\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/34